Package: gdistance
Type: Package
Title: Package gdistance: distances and movements on geographical grids
Version: 1.0
Date: 14-January-2010
Author: Jacob van Etten
Depends: raster, igraph, Matrix, methods, sp 
Maintainer: Jacob van Etten <jacobvanetten@yahoo.com>
Description: Calculate distances and other measures using models/algorithms for movements on geographic grids (least-cost path, random walk, randomises shortest paths).
